## Additional Terms for Trading Scripts

### Educational Purpose Disclaimer

All Pine Script indicators and strategies in this repository are provided for
educational and research purposes only. These scripts are:

- NOT financial advice
- NOT guaranteed to be profitable
- NOT suitable for all markets or conditions
- NOT tested for live trading environments

### Risk Disclaimer

Trading financial instruments involves substantial risk of loss and is not
suitable for every investor. Past performance is not indicative of future
results. Before using any script from this repository in live trading:

1. Thoroughly backtest on historical data
2. Paper trade extensively in real-time conditions
3. Understand all assumptions and limitations
4. Consult with qualified financial professionals
5. Never risk more capital than you can afford to lose

### No Warranty

The scripts are provided "as is" without warranty of any kind. The authors
and contributors:

- Make no representations about accuracy or reliability
- Are not responsible for any trading losses
- Are not liable for any damages arising from use
- Do not guarantee continued maintenance or updates

### User Responsibility

By using these scripts, you acknowledge that:

- You are solely responsible for your trading decisions
- You understand the risks involved in trading
- You have the knowledge and experience to use these tools appropriately
- You will not hold the authors or contributors liable for any losses

